    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW\u2019s S54 engineering. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six remains the pinnacle of high-revving performance, featuring individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double-VANOS system for optimal torque delivery across the powerband. Mechanically, this chassis has been fastidiously maintained; the subframe has been structurally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Every bushing is tight, the suspension geometry is true, and the compression numbers across all six cylinders are within factory tolerances. This is a true driver\u2019s specimen in concours-level condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
